# Summary
This documentation details the Amplitude Data integration with Planhat, allowing real-time streaming of user activity events to Planhat's customer platform. The integration matches Amplitude user_ids with Planhat externalIds, requires admin access to a paid Planhat plan, and supports mapping of user identifiers and properties to enhance customer health scoring, segmentation, and workflow automation.

